Version 1.0.1 - 2010-09-18

	* Changed the config and data paths to conform the XDG standard

	* Limiting the maximum history size

	* Included option to cleanup the database

	* Small performance improvements

	* Implemented deletion of clip from database pressing delete from clip row

	* Added config options to enable/disable read/write from primary and clipboard selections

	* Added a config option to show/hide the window decoration on the gui


Version 1.0.0 - 2010-08-01

	* First version of Anamnesis

